title: Italissimo by Quicker's
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Italian, Fast food, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Italian take away at Frankfurt Airport Terminal 1 between A21 und A23. Offers coffee and sandwiches. Has a vegan sandwich with antipasti which is designated as vegan and also the possibility for latte with soy milk. A few seats.
